metadata.name: Kiba Inu Genesis #1
metadata.description: The Kiba Inu Genesis NFT collection is a collection of 111 unique 3d KIBA NFTs— unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. The collection is based on several awesome traits, which makes every Kiba Inu Genesis NFT unique and exclusive.
